<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4667056>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4: Zygoribatula prima n. sp. A – dorsal view, legs removed; B – ventral view, legs and gnathosoma removed. Scale bar 100 µm." ;
