    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4667060>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5: Zygoribatula prima n. sp. A – lateral view of prodorsum, legs, gnathosoma and epimeral setae removed; B – rostrum; C – rostral setae; D – lamellar seta; E – sensillus; F – notogastral seta c1; G – notogastral seta c2; H – notogastral seta lm; I – notogastral seta h3; J – area porosa Aa; K – area porosa A1 (oblong form); L – area porosa A1 (round form); M – area porosa A2; N – genital plate, left; O – anal plate, left. Scale bar (A) 100 µm, scale bar (J+K+L+M) 10 µm, scale bars (B, C+D, E+F+G+H+I, N+O) 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4667060/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4667062>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6: Zygoribatula prima n. sp. A – subcapitulum; B – palp; C – chelicera; D – leg I, right, antiaxial view; E – leg IV, left, antiaxial view. Scale bars 20 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4667062/files/figure.png" ;
